'''Candice Orwell''' is an [[Wikipedia:English people|English]] actress/model who played the [[Naboo Royal Handmaiden|handmaiden]] [[Yané]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']].

She has been represented by [[Wikipedia:London|London]]-based modeling agencies [[Wikipedia:Storm Model Management|Storm Model Management]] and Reality Check Management.

Orwell was present at the Collectormania 15 convention in [[2009]].

